#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:40
msgid "文件"
msgstr "Files"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:43
msgid "Prefetch"
msgstr "Prefetch"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:44
msgid "预读取文件夹，用来存放系统已访问过的文件的预读信息，扩展名为PF。位置在 ``C:\\Windows\\Prefetch`` 。"
msgstr "The Prefetch folder stores prefetch information for files the system has accessed. Files use the PF extension. The location is ``C:\\Windows\\Prefetch``."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:47
msgid "JumpLists"
msgstr "JumpLists"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:48
msgid ""
"记录用户最近使用的文档和应用程序，方便用户快速跳转到指定文件，位置在 "
"``%APPDATA%\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Recent`` 。"
msgstr "Records recently used documents and applications so users can quickly jump to specified files. The location is ``%APPDATA%\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Recent``."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:51
msgid "Amcache / RecentFileCache.bcf"
msgstr "Amcache / RecentFileCache.bcf"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:52
msgid "Windows中的使用这两个文件来跟踪具有不同可执行文件的应用程序兼容性问题，它可用于确定可执行文件首次运行的时间和最后修改时间。"
msgstr "Windows uses these two files to track application compatibility issues for applications with different executables. They can be used to determine when an executable first ran and when it was last modified."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:54
msgid ""
"在Windows 7、Windows Server 2008 R2等系统中，文件保存在 "
"``C:\\Windows\\AppCompat\\Programs\\RecentFileCache.bcf`` "
"，包含程序的创建时间、上次修改时间、上次访问时间和文件名。"
msgstr "On Windows 7, Windows Server 2008 R2, and similar systems, the file is saved at ``C:\\Windows\\AppCompat\\Programs\\RecentFileCache.bcf`` and contains the program creation time, last modification time, last access time, and file name."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:56
msgid ""
"在Windows 8、Windows 10、Windows Server 2012等系统中，文件保存在 "
"``C:\\Windows\\AppCompat\\Programs\\Amcache.hve`` "
"，包含文件大小、版本、sha1、二进制文件类型等信息。"
msgstr "On Windows 8, Windows 10, Windows Server 2012, and similar systems, the file is saved at ``C:\\Windows\\AppCompat\\Programs\\Amcache.hve`` and contains information such as file size, version, SHA1, and binary file type."

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:59
msgid "时间轴"
msgstr "Timeline"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:60
msgid "Windows时间轴是Windows 10在1803版中引入的一个新特性，会记录访问过的网站、编辑过的文档、运行的程序等，"
msgstr "Windows Timeline is a new feature introduced in Windows 10 version 1803. It records visited websites, edited documents, executed programs, and so on,"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:63
msgid "彻底删除"
msgstr "Secure Deletion"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:64
msgid "多次覆写文件 ``cipher /w:<path>``"
msgstr "Overwrite files multiple times ``cipher /w:<path>``"

#: ../../source/intranet/windows/trace.rst:65
msgid "格式化某磁盘count次 ``format D: /P:<count>``"
msgstr "Format a disk `<count>` times ``format D: /P:<count>``"
